程式語言 : Apple開放用於多核CPU平行處理的Grand Central Dispatch



Grand Central Dispatch是Apple用於最新一版Mac OS 10.6的多核心平行處理技術，
期望讓OSX在面對多核心的環境下，可以在軟體處理上，更加平衡地運用硬體資源，
而現在Apple方面將此項技術以不依賴OSX 核心XNU的方式開放出來。

以下是slashdot的新聞擷取
引言:

    "Apple has open sourced libdispatch, also known as Grand Central
Dispatch, which is technology in Snow Leopard that makes it easier for
developers to take advantage of multi-core parallelism. Kernel support is
not required, but performance optimizations Apple made for supporting GCD
are visible in xnu. Block support in C is required and is currently
available in LLVM (note that Apple has submitted their implementation of C
blocks for standardization)."


全文網址
http://apple.slashdot.org/story/09/09/11/1139212/Apple-Open-Sources-Grand-Central-Dispatch

GCD技術的開放原始碼版本稱為libdispatch，以下是其官方網站，以Apache
2.0方式發佈
http://libdispatch.macosforge.org/ 
